# Implementation Plan - Simple Prototype Scene

## Goal
Create a new, simplified game scene (`simple_prototype.tscn`) that demonstrates the core "Web of Fate" mechanics (Draw, Place, Resolve) without the complexity of meta-progression, shops, or advanced UI overlays.

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> This will create a new scene and script independent of the main game flow. It is intended for testing and verifying core mechanics.

## Proposed Changes

### New Files

#### [NEW] [SimplePrototypeController.gd](file:///C:/Users/Lutfi/Desktop/Godot/Assets/simple-card-pile-ui-master/simple-card-pile-ui-master/simple-card-pile-ui-master/web_of_fate/scripts/SimplePrototypeController.gd)
- A stripped-down version of [SimpleGameController.gd](file:///C:/Users/Lutfi/Desktop/Godot/Assets/simple-card-pile-ui-master/simple-card-pile-ui-master/simple-card-pile-ui-master/web_of_fate/scripts/SimpleGameController.gd).
- **Features:**
    - Initialize 5 slots (TL, TR, BL, BR, Center).
    - Manage Deck and Hand (Draw 8 cards).
