    - Handle Spread Resolution (Trigger `GameManager.resolve_spread`).
    - Basic UI updates (Chaos, Legacy labels).
- **Omitted:**
    - Shop System.
    - Grimoire/Collection UI.
    - Progression/Unlocks.
    - Complex Juice effects (kept minimal).

#### [NEW] [simple_prototype.tscn](file:///C:/Users/Lutfi/Desktop/Godot/Assets/simple-card-pile-ui-master/simple-card-pile-ui-master/simple-card-pile-ui-master/web_of_fate/scenes/simple_prototype.tscn)
